ÃWS: Amazon Web Service

Terraform --> a framework to deploy CI/CD to AWS

basic aws commands:
  # aws runs on bash shell
  bash

  # upload/download file
  aws s3 cp 

  # sync folder
  aws s3 sync ./local-folder s3://my0bucket/folder/

  # create new bucket
  aws s3 mb s3://my-new-bucket

  # delete bucket
  aws s3 rb s3://my-bucket --force

  # more
  aws s3 ls
  aws s3 ls s3://my-bucket/
  aws s3 rm s3://my-bucket/file.txt
  aws s3 rm s3://my-bucket/folder/ --recursive
